{"id":225,"parent_id":224,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":225,"title":"Mormon 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Morm.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","The Book of Mormon"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Ammaron instructs Mormon concerning the sacred records—War commences between the Nephites and the Lamanites—The Three Nephites are taken away—Wickedness, unbelief, sorceries, and witchcraft prevail. About",["span.small","A.D."],"321–326."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.1","order":"05.24.001.23733"},["b","1"],"And now I, Mormon, make a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"record"],"of the things which I have both seen and heard, and call it the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Book of Mormon"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.2","order":"05.24.001.23734"},["b","2"],"And about the time that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Ammaron"],"hid up the records unto the Lord, he came unto me, (I being about ten years of age, and I began to be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"learned"],"somewhat after the manner of the learning of my people) and Ammaron said unto me: I perceive that thou art a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"sober"],"child, and art quick to observe;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.3","order":"05.24.001.23735"},["b","3"],"Therefore, when ye are about twenty and four years old I would that ye should remember the things that ye have observed concerning this people; and when ye are of that age go to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"land Antum"],", unto a hill which shall be called",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Shim"],"; and there have I deposited unto the Lord all the sacred engravings concerning this people."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.4","order":"05.24.001.23736"},["b","4"],"And behold, ye shall take the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"plates of Nephi"],"unto yourself, and the remainder shall ye leave in the place where they are; and ye shall engrave on the plates of Nephi all the things that ye have observed concerning this people."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.5","order":"05.24.001.23737"},["b","5"],"And I, Mormon, being a descendant of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Nephi"],", (and my father’s name was Mormon) I remembered the things which Ammaron commanded me."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.6","order":"05.24.001.23738"},["b","6"],"And it came to pass that I, being eleven years old, was carried by my father into the land southward, even to the land of Zarahemla."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.7","order":"05.24.001.23739"},["b","7"],"The whole face of the land had become covered with buildings, and the people were as numerous almost, as it were the sand of the sea."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.8","order":"05.24.001.23740"},["b","8"],"And it came to pass in this year there began to be a war between the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Nephites"],", who consisted of the Nephites and the Jacobites and the Josephites and the Zoramites; and this war was between the Nephites, and the Lamanites and the Lemuelites and the Ishmaelites."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.9","order":"05.24.001.23741"},["b","9"],"Now the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Lamanites"],"and the Lemuelites and the Ishmaelites were called Lamanites, and the two parties were Nephites and Lamanites."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.10","order":"05.24.001.23742"},["b","10"],"And it came to pass that the war began to be among them in the borders of Zarahemla, by the waters of Sidon."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.11","order":"05.24.001.23743"},["b","11"],"And it came to pass that the Nephites had gathered together a great number of men, even to exceed the number of thirty thousand. And it came to pass that they did have in this same year a number of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"battles"],", in which the Nephites did beat the Lamanites and did slay many of them."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.12","order":"05.24.001.23744"},["b","12"],"And it came to pass that the Lamanites withdrew their design, and there was peace settled in the land; and peace did remain for the space of about four years, that there was no bloodshed."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.13","order":"05.24.001.23745"},["b","13"],"But wickedness did prevail upon the face of the whole land, insomuch that the Lord did take away his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"beloved"],"disciples, and the work of miracles and of healing did cease because of the iniquity of the people."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.14","order":"05.24.001.23746"},["b","14"],"And there were no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"gifts"],"from the Lord, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Holy Ghost"],"did not come upon any, because of their wickedness and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.15","order":"05.24.001.23747"},["b","15"],"And I, being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"fifteen"],"years of age and being somewhat of a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"sober"],"mind, therefore I was",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"visited"],"of the Lord, and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"tasted"],"and knew of the goodness of Jesus."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.16","order":"05.24.001.23748"},["b","16"],"And I did endeavor to preach unto this people, but my mouth was shut, and I was forbidden that I should preach unto them; for behold they had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"wilfully rebelled"],"against their God; and the beloved disciples were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"taken"],"away out of the land, because of their iniquity."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.17","order":"05.24.001.23749"},["b","17"],"But I did remain among them, but I was forbidden to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"preach"],"unto them, because of the hardness of their hearts; and because of the hardness of their hearts the land was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"cursed"],"for their sake."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.18","order":"05.24.001.23750"},["b","18"],"And these Gadianton robbers, who were among the Lamanites, did infest the land, insomuch that the inhabitants thereof began to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"hide"],"up their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"treasures"],"in the earth; and they became slippery, because the Lord had cursed the land, that they could not hold them, nor retain them again."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.19","order":"05.24.001.23751"},["b","19"],"And it came to pass that there were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"sorceries"],", and witchcrafts, and magics; and the power of the evil one was wrought upon all the face of the land, even unto the fulfilling of all the words of Abinadi, and also",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Samuel the Lamanite"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.1a","order":"05.24.001.23752"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/5.11.11-18"},"3 Ne. 5:11 (11–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.5"},"Morm. 8:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.1b","order":"05.24.001.23754"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/w-of-m/1.5"},"W of M 1:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.9"},"Morm. 5:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.2a","order":"05.24.001.23756"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/4-ne/1.48.47-49"},"4 Ne. 1:48 (47–49)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.2b","order":"05.24.001.23758"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"h